Interface Request

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractBindRequest, AbstractExtendedRequest, AnonymousSASLBindRequest, CancelRequest, CRAMMD5SASLBindRequest, DigestMD5SASLBindRequest, ExternalSASLBindRequest, GenericSASLBindRequest, GetConnectionIDRequest, GetSymmetricKeyRequest, GSSAPISASLBindRequest, PasswordModifyRequest, PasswordPolicyStateExtendedOperation.Request, PlainSASLBindRequest, SASLBindRequest, StartTLSRequest, WhoAmIRequest
public interface Request

The base class of all Requests provides methods for querying and manipulating the set of Controls included with a Request.
